{"tid":1803970,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Frontend 撚就黎收得皮","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T05:43:08.000Z","uid":236300,"like":10,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a320d2f87247b8d2b33835a06156acf72d1aa2e5","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"先奇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲用乜撚 wordpress，公司出左個類似 wordpress 既 tool，目標係助 frontend 撚甩苦海，收 wordpress 皮！<br />\n<br />\n1. 支援 restful api<br />\n2. 支援 html + javascript 自定義版面<br />\n3. git push 自動部署版面更新<br />\n4. 有 dynamic 既 article &amp; product query engine(advanced 既 query filter)<br />\n5. 支援 production &amp; testing 環境<br />\n6. 支援 custom domain parking<br />\n<br />\n有 SDK，不過暫時得 js 同 node.js 版<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/osltd/oneshop-web.js\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fosltd%2Foneshop-web.js&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=2b286a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/osltd/oneshop-web.js</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/osltd/oneshop.js\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fosltd%2Foneshop.js&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=b634cfa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/osltd/oneshop.js</a><br />\n<br />\n有片有教學<br />\n免費開 shop/website:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YjEhv97633Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYjEhv97633Y&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=11aaedec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YjEhv97633Y</a><br />\n<br />\n連接 Github 整 custom theme:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CPEyCSblJb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCPEyCSblJb4&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=cd750052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CPEyCSblJb4</a><br />\n<br />\n淨係用 html &amp; javascript 整 custom theme:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ej2FloWjxNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fej2FloWjxNQ&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=2c2135ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ej2FloWjxNQ</a><br />\n<br />\n用 React 整 theme:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Bb2disDOY28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBb2disDOY28&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=371b25a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Bb2disDOY28</a><br />\n<br />\n用 React 整 article list:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YZvBrarCyVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYZvBrarCyVc&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=72118028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YZvBrarCyVc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲用乜撚野 wordpress 係到殘害自己生命，搞撚到自己戇鳩鳩咁！幫手試下，支持呢個 tool 即係支持你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免費開網站要用referral code：<br />\nURL: <a href=\"https://panel.oneshop.cloud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpanel.oneshop.cloud&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=bcb7f938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://panel.oneshop.cloud</a><br />\nreferral code: 5k7VI80G5PahWsgm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界咁撚多免費 themes，唔係唔識搵呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://colorlib.com/wp/free-html-website-templates/#free-html-templates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcolorlib.com%2Fwp%2Ffree-html-website-templates%2F%23free-html-templates&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F