},{"pid":"fd4c0ae17499b893abce1ce7a9cb5f09d19fb8fe","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"唔識用wp唔係wp既錯"},{"pid":"15a82a8a866aa81ebcc1a0cec1c3847e09b0efe2","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b632399524e55e1ccc2cebb566431c472d3117","tid":1803970,"uid":23953,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jEmPht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jEmPht.png&h=97a1cf8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWordPress killer<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"我真係好鐘意呢張圖。<br />\n當日 iPhone (2G ，連 App Store 都冇）出個陣，好多人話佢冇手寫筆，冇鍵盤，冇呢樣，冇果樣，而 Nokia 、Motorola 都用呢幾個「論點」去攻擊 iPhone 。<br />\n時間會證明一切。"},{"pid":"cfa9ee87e675f95239cb40f71325dfe4a438a857","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4c0ae17499b893abce1ce7a9cb5f09d19fb8fe","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"唔識用wp唔係wp既錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"可以分享下？<br />\n都有聽過pro ge 人話WP 唔太啱做e-commerce platform, 話Server workload 太重"},{"pid":"07cbb4a558aa5e15d639fb397c8b2d975332a666","tid":1803970,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"flutter唔係更好？"},{"pid":"2f5668c644b48825da89d2c12999b7771ce8894f","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa9ee87e675f95239cb40f71325dfe4a438a857","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4c0ae17499b893abce1ce7a9cb5f09d19fb8fe","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"唔識用wp唔係wp既錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"可以分享下？<br />\n都有聽過pro ge 人話WP 唔太啱做e-commerce platform, 話Server workload 太重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"大型既magento啦<br />\n<br />\n中少型既，睇你點optimize <br />\n<br />\n用咩方法做都要optimize嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n自己framework寫都可以慢嫁"},{"pid":"6f8012ab8b734900fad4504ba7de1720a3c878e6","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07cbb4a558aa5e15d639fb397c8b2d975332a666","tid":1803970,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"flutter唔係更好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"正好最近玩緊 Flutter ，係幾有趣既 framework ，亦有好多原生既野（UI 接近唔使諗，點寫都係 Material UI 風格）。<br />\n佢概念萬物皆 Widget 是有趣的，你需要熟讀份 Doc 先有效率咁寫到，但同時你熟讀左就寫基本野冇任何難度。<br />\n<br />\n但 Flutter 都係做唔到太複雜既野，都需要有一個 Backend 幫你手。"},{"pid":"d3601b81c0a79d8344e35528e4ef57786857679c","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5668c644b48825da89d2c12999b7771ce8894f","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa9ee87e675f95239cb40f71325dfe4a438a857","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4c0ae17499b893abce1ce7a9cb5f09d19fb8fe","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"唔識用wp唔係wp既錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"可以分享下？<br />\n都有聽過pro ge 人話WP 唔太啱做e-commerce platform, 話Server workload 太重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"大型既magento啦<br />\n<br />\n中少型既，睇你點optimize <br />\n<br />\n用咩方法做都要optimize嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n自己framework寫都可以慢嫁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"Magento<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOptimize 應該就係重點<br />\n因為啲WP人成日話，米又係PHP。<br />\n花時間去學Magento, 不如花時間學optimize 個WP好過<br />\n<br />\n再利申： JAMStack 研究中"},{"pid":"0a547c1b51911f469cbd89b7d906f242a900e16a","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ad2926a3b11251575e7328578b6b8368052062","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96be0c1d4ddec4c958a83437848895f5babf4833","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8fe5b179911fdddc9c8103396b7faf2867fd614b","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n可以比較下Pros 同cons<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:38:39.000Z","msg":"1. 支援 restful api<br />\n2. 支援 html + javascript 自定義版面 (wordpress 一撚定要用埋 php)<br />\n3. git push 自動部署版面更新 (wordpress 有撚)<br />\n4. 有 dynamic 既 article &amp; product query engine(advanced 既 query filter)<br />\n5. 支援 production &amp; testing 環境 (wordpress 呢？)<br />\n6. 支援 custom domain parking<br />\n7. 有 cdn server 搞 image resizer (wordpress 呢？)<br />\n8. SSR 上 wordpress 係有 PHP redner，但呢個用其他方法 handle，就算用 react 寫都有 SEO"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"CMS 方面呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申： JAMStack 研究中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2U7r0za.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2U7r0za.png&h=a1fee752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gz6f7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gz6f7v.png&h=86e2e3e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ede1a2fca05492ec7b23e4e30af8f849001f283","tid":1803970,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4864faa6e76861ebc0f4b52bc7a5f92cfcd1eb","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c412de03b9a3e2e6b39d8556a3afdfb85f98fd0d","tid":1803970,"uid":46761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"好似幾吸引<br />\n一直搵緊個decoupled ge cms可以做晒web同mobile<br />\n又可以做埋e-shop<br />\n利申以前做過好多Wordpress project<br />\n講真同成個格硬整冇分別<br />\n啲公司都係買theme改<br />\n啲css js全部外掛<br />\n個site唔洗講緊係慢到閪咁<br />\n真係不可一不可再<br />\n<br />\n不過個platform夠唔夠flexible架？<br />\n例如我要儲好多唔同entries而唔係純articles/products,<br />\n呢方面會唔會support?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://carlig.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcarlig.com&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=fe0f4ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://carlig.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lkf.tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flkf.tv&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=95ce6d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lkf.tv</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://kumo.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkumo.com.hk&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=c362c180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kumo.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\narticle 個 api 有一個 filter -- sections, 用法係:<br />\n/api/articles?sections[name*]=llo<br />\n/api/articles?sections[type]=abc,test<br />\n<br />\nproduct api filter, 用法係:<br />\n/api/merchandises?variants[size]=s,m,l<br />\n/api/merchandises?variants[color]=blue<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/api/articles 係 for public<br />\n/api/feeds 係 private, 要login 左先用到"},{"pid":"01f84d2dc84d9c26929f9a1e82dbd6d96e5139c4","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3601b81c0a79d8344e35528e4ef57786857679c","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5668c644b48825da89d2c12999b7771ce8894f","tid":1803970,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa9ee87e675f95239cb40f71325dfe4a438a857","tid":1803970,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"可以分享下？<br />\n都有聽過pro ge 人話WP 唔太啱做e-commerce platform, 話Server workload 太重"},"citedBy":1,"r