,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"flutter唔係更好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"正好最近玩緊 Flutter ，係幾有趣既 framework ，亦有好多原生既野（UI 接近唔使諗，點寫都係 Material UI 風格）。<br />\n佢概念萬物皆 Widget 是有趣的，你需要熟讀份 Doc 先有效率咁寫到，但同時你熟讀左就寫基本野冇任何難度。<br />\n<br />\n但 Flutter 都係做唔到太複雜既野，都需要有一個 Backend 幫你手。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"重點係安全問題：frontend 擺喺client度。你永遠冇辦法保證d資訊係安全，個client裝佐落去後有冇再加料。<br />\n<br />\n所以frontend 永遠只會提供剛好需要的資訊。處理敏感資料一定係交番俾backend做。"},{"pid":"9c4ec800754a8dcf3d51380408d85798f24838df","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb93a110eafe930c149759790e729eeac91bb31","tid":1803970,"uid":34961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"010719b85c6659c2bff1092f6ca11d0974eaa28d","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ddd6ad16dcbbaa5ab499404b5fb7d4d309a2ad1","tid":1803970,"uid":34961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"self hosting?<br />\n用邊隻DB?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"BaaS, private cloud 要用 corp package."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"即係所有野都要cloud而冇得放係自己既vpc?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"on-premise installation 要 corp package 先有."},{"pid":"171b9747153147eba6a94b32137018140a769ee9","tid":1803970,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T18:07:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a2993260cd77b4fde46c06d50565032e0b8fd665","tid":1803970,"uid":236300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c412de03b9a3e2e6b39d8556a3afdfb85f98fd0d","tid":1803970,"uid":46761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"好似幾吸引<br />\n一直搵緊個decoupled ge cms可以做晒web同mobile<br />\n又可以做埋e-shop<br />\n利申以前做過好多Wordpress project<br />\n講真同成個格硬整冇分別<br />\n啲公司都係買theme改<br />\n啲css js全部外掛<br />\n個site唔洗講緊係慢到閪咁<br />\n真係不可一不可再<br />\n<br />\